Description: # ocrd-page-to-alto
        
        > Convert PAGE (v. 2019) to ALTO (v. 2.0 - 4.2)
        
        [![image](https://circleci.com/gh/kba/page-to-alto.svg?style=svg)](https://circleci.com/gh/kba/page-to-alto)
        
